snippet.title: Amber Heard FREAKS OUT on Johnny Depp's LAWYER! New COURT documents!
snippet.description:
#JusticeForJohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp
Johnny Depp's lawyer Adam Waldman is giving Amber Heard a run for her money. Heard continues to become frustrated with Waldman's presence on Twitter. In this video I discuss NEW(at least to me) documents that have been found.

Links:

https://twitter.com/tasteofsanity/status/1309568044608479232
CHAPTERS:
Document #1: 0:58
Document #2: 2:00

Disclaimer: I cannot prove in this video nor other videos if all of this information is 100% without a doubt true. I personally believe it to be true but I can't entirely prove that.
